Create the microservice application: calculator-app  using starter-spring.io

Create the following rest controller:GetMapping

1) /add (request parameter a,request parameter b)

return  a+b;

Example: @GetMapping("/add")
             public double add(@RequestParam("a") double a,@RequestParam("b") double b){
                 return a+b;
             }

2) /sub (request parameter a,request parameter b)

return  a-b;

3) /mul (request parameter a,request parameter b)

return  a*b;

4) /div (request parameter a,request parameter b)

return  a/b;

Create the read me file and update the folowings

Build application

start application

swagger url

Note: create the two profiles (dev and prod)

dev: - apllication should run on port 8081
prod: - application should run on 8082

Add single securith

USER role : username: user123 password: password123